714
01:08:33.819 --> 01:08:35.527 line:82%
And we've intercepted
a message that...

715
01:08:35.777 --> 01:08:38.948 line:82%
...the Pakistani delegates are likely
to raise the Kashmir issue again.

716
01:08:39.152 --> 01:08:40.507 line:82%
Ever since then...

717
01:08:40.777 --> 01:08:44.797 line:82%
Mr. Shenoy has asked me to monitor
every known Pakistani source.

718
01:08:45.027 --> 01:08:50.784 line:82%
And for the past 20 days these random
messages have messed up my mind.

719
01:08:51.486 --> 01:08:54.828 line:82%
To make things worse... they have set
their codes based on our film stars.

720
01:08:55.277 --> 01:08:58.442 line:82%
Tell me, who is supposed to be
Mallika Sherawat in the government?

721
01:08:58.647 --> 01:09:00.861 line:82%
I understand if they say
Gulshan Grover or Amrish Puri.

722
01:09:01.319 --> 01:09:04.312 line:82%
And not just films...
they are now into television as well.

723
01:09:04.611 --> 01:09:09.368 line:82%
