and Pakistan Foreign Ministers...

740
01:10:36.236 --> 01:10:39.625 line:82%
On the sidelines of the UN Foreign
Ministers' Meeting at Istanbul...

741
01:10:40.156 --> 01:10:43.339 line:82%
