London and get here.

856
01:25:10.276 --> 01:25:11.818 line:82%
Which bank has he withdrawn
the money from?

857
01:25:12.609 --> 01:25:13.651 line:82%
How much?

858
01:25:13.832 --> 01:25:16.359 line:82%
Sir... a total of 47 thousand
dollars, sir.

859
01:25:16.831 --> 01:25:19.484 line:82%
47 thousand dollars?

860
01:25:20.442 --> 01:25:21.942 line:82%
Sir... about 2.3 million Rupees.

861
01:25:26.401 --> 01:25:27.401 line:82%
Should be 2.3 million.

862
01:25:27.651 --> 01:25:31.961 line:82%
